# EzHash
CLI tool which computes and compares file hash.

## Usage

Basic:
```
ezh sha256 ~/Downloads/image.iso 
```

With comparison:
```
ezh sha256 ~/Downloads/image.iso 85dcd0455f6bb643c4ddd819a0b0c4737d850f6df3b9ec2686bc6b7cd71791f7
```

